title: Sake Yeast Sheet Mask Review
description:
From the My Beauty Diary collection of sheet masks, I'm reviewing the first one I tried and it's the Sake Yeast. All the information about the mask is in the video and it's good for all skin types. I would recommend this mask to those with oily skin, with acne scars, or dull skin. I bought these masks from http://imomoko.com/ with my own money and these are my honest opinions about the product. All of the factual info about the mask I retrieved from their website.
As I said at the end of the vid, if you want me to review a specfic mask sooner please go to my imomoko haul vid where I list the ones I have and I'll and if you tell me in a comment below or on that vid I'll definitely fulfill ur request. :)
You can find my haul vid here: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PCZJJ-WzKp0
